					<div class="entry-content">
						<h2 style="text-align: center;"><meta name="google-site-verification" content="u65YB1jGW3nwuUphEgvv9PUlPVn1qxHJe4jC0BFngs0" /></h2>
<p>Welcome to the Federation of British Columbia Writers, a community committed to providingÂ support and assistance to its members, and writers across the province. We may post a few important upcoming events on this page, but otherwise please check our BC Writers Calendar on the right for information on what&#8217;s happening. For information on writing groups, membership benefits, resources for writers, information on our publications, and more, please check our menu bar above. If you have any questions, please feel free to <a href="http://www.bcwriters.ca/contact-us-2/">contact us</a>.</p>
<p>Happy writing!</p>
